OL,3,CHealth risks of climate change reach
OL,4,Crecord breaking levels, experts warn
OL,6,FPeople in the UK are increasingly
OL,7,Fexposed to dangerous extreme heat, as
OL,8,Fglobal health threats of climate
OL,9,Fchange reach record-breaking levels,
OL,10,Fexperts warn.
OL,12,FAround the world in 2023, people were
OL,13,Fexposed to an average 50 more days of
OL,14,Fhealth-threatening temperatures than
OL,15,Fwould be expected without climate
OL,16,Fchange, while extreme drought affected
OL,17,F48% of global land area, the latest
OL,18,FLancet Countdown on Health and Climate
OL,19,FChange report said.
