OL,3,CHealth risks of climate change reach
OL,4,Crecord breaking levels, experts warn
OL,6,FIn the UK, people are increasingly
OL,7,Fexposed to health-threatening extreme
OL,8,Fheat, raising the risk of heat-related
OL,9,Fillness and mortality, with an extra
OL,10,Fnine deaths per 100,000 people on
OL,11,Faverage in 2013-2022.
OL,13,FEvery infant and adult over 65 was
OL,14,Fexposed to an average 6.5 days of
OL,15,Fheatwaves a year between 2014-2023,
OL,16,Fwhile 8.5 million potential labour
OL,17,Fhours were lost to extreme heat in
OL,18,F2023, up 166% from the 1990s average,
OL,19,Fwith construction workers hardest hit,
OL,20,Fthe report warns.
