OL,3,CHealth risks of climate change reach
OL,4,Crecord breaking levels, experts warn
OL,6,FThe report also warns that people's
OL,7,Fhealth in the UK was being hit by air
OL,8,Fpollution, with 29,500 deaths in 2021,
OL,9,Fwith fossil fuels contributing to 44%
OL,10,Fof those cases, and early deaths
OL,11,Fcosting #70 billion ` but shifting
OL,12,Ftowards zero emissions and clean
OL,13,Fenergy could tackle climate and health
OL,14,Fproblems.
OL,16,FAnd unhealthy, unsustainable diets are
OL,17,Fcontributing to greenhouse gas
OL,18,Femissions and hitting health, but a
OL,19,Fshift to more balanced diets would
OL,20,Freduce deaths and tackle climate
OL,21,Fchange, the report argues.
