OL,3,CHealth risks of climate change reach
OL,4,Crecord breaking levels, experts warn
OL,6,FThe report finds that 10 of the 15
OL,7,Findicators tracking health threats of
OL,8,Fclimate change have reached new record
OL,9,Flevels.
OL,11,FThe report's authors accuse
OL,12,Fgovernments and companies of
OL,13,Fcontinuing to fuel the fire by
OL,14,Finvesting in fossil fuels, and say the
OL,15,Ftrillions of dollars spent funding
OL,16,Foil, gas and coal should be redirected
OL,17,Fto the shift into clean economies.
