OL,3,CHealth risks of climate change reach
OL,4,Crecord breaking levels, experts warn
OL,6,FDr Marina Romanello, executive
OL,7,Fdirector of the Lancet Countdown at
OL,8,FUniversity College London, said the
OL,9,Ffindings, released as countries
OL,10,Fprepare to meet for the next round of
OL,11,FUN climate negotiations in fossil-fuel
OL,12,Frich Azerbaijan, were the most
OL,13,Fconcerning in the eight years of the
OL,14,Freport.
OL,16,F"Once again, last year broke climate
OL,17,Fchange records`with extreme heat
OL,18,Fwaves, deadly weather events, and
OL,19,Fdevastating wildfires affecting people
OL,20,Faround the world," she said.
